[30;1m39 | [0m[35m    component. A lightweight component is a self-contained Python function that[0m
[30;1m40 | [0m[35m    includes all necessary imports and dependencies. In lightweight components,[0m
[30;1m41 | [0m[35m    ``packages_to_install`` will be used to install dependencies at runtime. The[0m
[30;1m42 | [0m[35m    parameters ``install_kfp_package`` and ``kfp_package_path`` can be used to control[0m
[30;1m43 | [0m[35m    how and from where KFP should be installed when the lightweight component is executed.[0m
